What happens when the CLARITY Act passes?

@Collin_McCune points to the “absolute explosion of activity” following stablecoin legislation:

“The most important thing that people miss about why clarity is so important is: It is a signal.”

“It’s a signal that America is here, and they’ve made a long-term decision.”

@milkroaddaily

